{"title":"Fancy Upgrades to State 4130 Flat Bar All-Road Bike, plus Gravel Groupset Sneak Peeks","link":"https://bikerumor.com/fancy-upgrades-to-state-4130-flat-bar-all-road-bike-plus-gravel-groupset-sneak-peeks/","date":1684346138000,"content":"<p>Hot on the heels of the limited <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/doves-cry-new-state-4130-purple-reign-all-road-ss/\" target=\"_blank\">Purple Reign</a> single-speed we lusted over yesterday, State Bicycle Co. has more news of <a href=\"https://www.statebicycle.com/collections/off-road-bikes/products/4130-all-road-flat-bar-matte-olive-650b-700c\" target=\"_blank\">awesome upgrades</a> to the 4130 Flat Bar All-Road. New colors and some pretty major mechanical upgrades are now available on this affordable and value-packed bicycle that State says is the perfect bike for gravel and/or touring. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>It might even mean an all-new affordable State Bicycle Co. Gravel 1 Group-Set could be just around the corner!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>State Bicycle Co. 4130 Flat Bar All-Road bike</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-4130-Flat-Bar-All-Road-Rust-to-Black.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-4130-Flat-Bar-All-Road-Rust-to-Black-800x533.jpeg\" alt=\"State 4130 Flat Bar All-Road Rust to Black\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-4130-Flat-Bar-All-Road-Rust-to-Black-800x533.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-4130-Flat-Bar-All-Road-Rust-to-Black-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-4130-Flat-Bar-All-Road-Rust-to-Black-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-4130-Flat-Bar-All-Road-Rust-to-Black-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-4130-Flat-Bar-All-Road-Rust-to-Black-720x480.jpeg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-4130-Flat-Bar-All-Road-Rust-to-Black.jpeg 1280w\" /></a><figcaption><em>all c. State Bicycle Co</em>. –  new Rust to Black Fade</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The two new handsome colorways are Rust to Black fade, the name of this color (sounds kinda metal and reminds me of that Neil Young <a href=\"https://youtu.be/UDTx0JQlXRY\" target=\"_blank\">song</a>).</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-4130-Flat-Bar-All-Road-turquoise-fat-tire-side-shot.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-4130-Flat-Bar-All-Road-turquoise-fat-tire-side-shot-800x533.jpeg\" alt=\"State 4130 Flat Bar All-Road turquoise fat tire side shot\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-4130-Flat-Bar-All-Road-turquoise-fat-tire-side-shot-800x533.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-4130-Flat-Bar-All-Road-turquoise-fat-tire-side-shot-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-4130-Flat-Bar-All-Road-turquoise-fat-tire-side-shot-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-4130-Flat-Bar-All-Road-turquoise-fat-tire-side-shot-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-4130-Flat-Bar-All-Road-turquoise-fat-tire-side-shot-720x480.jpeg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-4130-Flat-Bar-All-Road-turquoise-fat-tire-side-shot.jpeg 1280w\" /></a><figcaption>Turquoise to Black Fade</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Any who, the other color is called Turquoise to Black fade, not as metal sounding, but still very handsome.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>What’s new?</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-4130-Flat-Bar-All-Road-hydro-brakes.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-4130-Flat-Bar-All-Road-hydro-brakes-800x533.jpeg\" alt=\"State 4130 Flat Bar All-Road hydro brakes\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-4130-Flat-Bar-All-Road-hydro-brakes-800x533.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-4130-Flat-Bar-All-Road-hydro-brakes-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-4130-Flat-Bar-All-Road-hydro-brakes-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-4130-Flat-Bar-All-Road-hydro-brakes-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-4130-Flat-Bar-All-Road-hydro-brakes-720x480.jpeg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-4130-Flat-Bar-All-Road-hydro-brakes.jpeg 1280w\" /></a><figcaption>Mineral oil hydraulic brakes</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-4130-Flat-Bar-All-Road-clutched-rear-deralilleur.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-4130-Flat-Bar-All-Road-clutched-rear-deralilleur-800x533.jpeg\" alt=\"State 4130 Flat Bar All-Road clutched rear deralilleur\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-4130-Flat-Bar-All-Road-clutched-rear-deralilleur-800x533.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-4130-Flat-Bar-All-Road-clutched-rear-deralilleur-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-4130-Flat-Bar-All-Road-clutched-rear-deralilleur-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-4130-Flat-Bar-All-Road-clutched-rear-deralilleur-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-4130-Flat-Bar-All-Road-clutched-rear-deralilleur-720x480.jpeg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-4130-Flat-Bar-All-Road-clutched-rear-deralilleur.jpeg 1280w\" /></a><figcaption>Adjustable clutched rear derailleur</figcaption></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Some of the mechanical upgrades come in the form of new hydraulic brakes, and an all-new rear derailleur, pushing the 4130 All-Road’s bang-for-your-buck factor up a few notches.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Wait what?</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Tech Details – Gravel Group-Set Tease!</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-Bicycle-Co-4130-Flat-Bar-All-Road-bike_all-new-mineral-oil-hydraulic-flat-mount-disc-brakes.jpg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-Bicycle-Co-4130-Flat-Bar-All-Road-bike_all-new-mineral-oil-hydraulic-flat-mount-disc-brakes-800x533.jpg\" alt=\"State Bicycle Co 4130 Flat Bar All-Road bike, flat mount hydraulic disc brakes\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-Bicycle-Co-4130-Flat-Bar-All-Road-bike_all-new-mineral-oil-hydraulic-flat-mount-disc-brakes-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-Bicycle-Co-4130-Flat-Bar-All-Road-bike_all-new-mineral-oil-hydraulic-flat-mount-disc-brakes-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-Bicycle-Co-4130-Flat-Bar-All-Road-bike_all-new-mineral-oil-hydraulic-flat-mount-disc-brakes-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-Bicycle-Co-4130-Flat-Bar-All-Road-bike_all-new-mineral-oil-hydraulic-flat-mount-disc-brakes-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-Bicycle-Co-4130-Flat-Bar-All-Road-bike_all-new-mineral-oil-hydraulic-flat-mount-disc-brakes-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-Bicycle-Co-4130-Flat-Bar-All-Road-bike_all-new-mineral-oil-hydraulic-flat-mount-disc-brakes-720x480.jpg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-Bicycle-Co-4130-Flat-Bar-All-Road-bike_all-new-mineral-oil-hydraulic-flat-mount-disc-brakes.jpg 1800w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Yes, State now has their own branded mineral oil hydraulic flat-mount disc brakes. For now they are only paired with those entry-level Shimano-esque flat bar mountain bike brake levers, but we can only imagine the State would want to offer a drop bar version of their new hydraulic disc brakes to lower costs compared to their more halo SRAM AXS gravel bike builds!</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-Bicycle-Co-4130-Flat-Bar-All-Road-bike_upgraded-1x11-mechanical-gravel-dereilleur-with-adjustable-clutch.jpg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-Bicycle-Co-4130-Flat-Bar-All-Road-bike_upgraded-1x11-mechanical-gravel-dereilleur-with-adjustable-clutch-800x533.jpg\" alt=\"State Bicycle Co 4130 Flat Bar All-Road bike, adjustable clutch 1x11 gravel derailleur\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-Bicycle-Co-4130-Flat-Bar-All-Road-bike_upgraded-1x11-mechanical-gravel-dereilleur-with-adjustable-clutch-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-Bicycle-Co-4130-Flat-Bar-All-Road-bike_upgraded-1x11-mechanical-gravel-dereilleur-with-adjustable-clutch-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-Bicycle-Co-4130-Flat-Bar-All-Road-bike_upgraded-1x11-mechanical-gravel-dereilleur-with-adjustable-clutch-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-Bicycle-Co-4130-Flat-Bar-All-Road-bike_upgraded-1x11-mechanical-gravel-dereilleur-with-adjustable-clutch-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-Bicycle-Co-4130-Flat-Bar-All-Road-bike_upgraded-1x11-mechanical-gravel-dereilleur-with-adjustable-clutch-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-Bicycle-Co-4130-Flat-Bar-All-Road-bike_upgraded-1x11-mechanical-gravel-dereilleur-with-adjustable-clutch-720x480.jpg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-Bicycle-Co-4130-Flat-Bar-All-Road-bike_upgraded-1x11-mechanical-gravel-dereilleur-with-adjustable-clutch.jpg 2000w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>And yes, they have an all-new second generation of their wide-range 11-speed mechanical rear derailleur. Unlike their <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/state-bicycle-co-4130-all-road-rolls-in-with-their-own-1x11-gravel-component-group/\" target=\"_blank\">original self-branded drivetrain</a> a few years back, this new one has apparently been upgraded with an internally adjustable clutch so the rider can tune how much chain stabilization they actually need vs. the added drivetrain drag.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>State already offered their mechanical <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/state-bicycle-co-4130-all-road-rolls-in-with-their-own-1x11-gravel-component-group/\" target=\"_blank\">All-Road 1 Groupset</a> separately for just $350 – before it sold out. And this might hint at a similarly affordable Gravel version in the near future. Fingers crossed!</p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-4130-Flat-Bar-All-Road-skinny-tire-front.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-4130-Flat-Bar-All-Road-skinny-tire-front-800x533.jpeg\" alt=\"State 4130 Flat Bar All-Road skinny tire front\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-4130-Flat-Bar-All-Road-skinny-tire-front-800x533.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-4130-Flat-Bar-All-Road-skinny-tire-front-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-4130-Flat-Bar-All-Road-skinny-tire-front-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-4130-Flat-Bar-All-Road-skinny-tire-front-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-4130-Flat-Bar-All-Road-skinny-tire-front-720x480.jpeg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-4130-Flat-Bar-All-Road-skinny-tire-front.jpeg 1280w\" /></a><figcaption>700 x 38mm tires </figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-4130-Flat-Bar-All-Road-fat-tire-front.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-4130-Flat-Bar-All-Road-fat-tire-front-800x533.jpeg\" alt=\"State 4130 Flat Bar All-Road fat tire front\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-4130-Flat-Bar-All-Road-fat-tire-front-800x533.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-4130-Flat-Bar-All-Road-fat-tire-front-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-4130-Flat-Bar-All-Road-fat-tire-front-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-4130-Flat-Bar-All-Road-fat-tire-front-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-4130-Flat-Bar-All-Road-fat-tire-front-720x480.jpeg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-4130-Flat-Bar-All-Road-fat-tire-front.jpeg 1280w\" /></a><figcaption>650b x 2.1″ tires </figcaption></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<h2>State 4130 Flat Bar Features &amp; Pricing</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Retail: $900</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Frame: </strong>4130 Chromoly Steel with Thru-Axle Dropouts (12x142mm rear spacing) w/ 2 water bottle mounts, rear mounts for rack and/or fenders</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Fork:</strong> 4130 Chromoly Steel with Thru-Axle Dropouts (12x100mm fork spacing)<br />​and 5 sets of mounts for water bottles, accessories, fenders, or racks, or add the Carbon Fiber “<a href=\"https://www.statebicycle.com/collections/frames/products/state-bicycle-co-carbon-fiber-monster-gravel-fork\" target=\"_blank\">Monster Fork</a>” for $299.99</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Wheelset: </strong>\n<ul>\n<li>700c: Tubeless Capable Wheel Set w/ Vittoria Terreno Zero Tires, 38mm (tubeless ready)</li>\n\n\n\n<li>650b: Tubeless Capable Wheel Set w/ Vittoria Barzo Tires, 2.1″ (53mm)</li>\n\n\n\n<li>EXTRA COST OPTION: Order the SECOND wheel set with tires and tubes, plus matching hubs, cassette, and brake rotors. Receive DOUBLE the versatility for ONLY $399.99 more.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Handlebars:</strong> ​ State Bicycle Co. Black Label Riser Bars</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Brakes:</strong> ​ State Bicycle Co. All-Road 1 Flat-Mount Hydraulic Disc. w/ 160mm 6-Bolt Rotors</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Drive train:</strong> ​ State Bicycle Co. All-Road 1 1×11 Drivetrain w/ Trigger Shift\n<ul>\n<li>Crank – State Bicycle Co. All-Road 1 – 42t </li>\n\n\n\n<li>Cassette – 11-42t</li>\n\n\n\n<li>All-New Adjustable Clutch Rear Derailleur</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-4130-Flat-Bar-All-Road-turquoise-lean.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-4130-Flat-Bar-All-Road-turquoise-lean-800x533.jpeg\" alt=\"State 4130 Flat Bar All-Road turquoise lean\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-4130-Flat-Bar-All-Road-turquoise-lean-800x533.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-4130-Flat-Bar-All-Road-turquoise-lean-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-4130-Flat-Bar-All-Road-turquoise-lean-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-4130-Flat-Bar-All-Road-turquoise-lean-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-4130-Flat-Bar-All-Road-turquoise-lean-720x480.jpeg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/State-4130-Flat-Bar-All-Road-turquoise-lean.jpeg 1280w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><em><a href=\"https://www.statebicycle.com/\" target=\"_blank\">StateBicycle.com</a></em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/fancy-upgrades-to-state-4130-flat-bar-all-road-bike-plus-gravel-groupset-sneak-peeks/\">Fancy Upgrades to State 4130 Flat Bar All-Road Bike, plus Gravel Groupset Sneak Peeks</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Ron Frazelle","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"9c9e52531c6092e567916fedc135bc5379a50f5e81dee0c3709823436a440903","category":"Cycling"}